'''麥可·蘭斯·林恩'''（{{lang-en|Michael Lance Lynn}}，{{bd|1987年|5月12日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於芝加哥白襪。先前他曾效力過紅雀、雙城、洋基與遊騎兵等隊。
==職業生涯==
===聖路易紅雀===
====2011年–2013年====
2011年6月2日，林恩登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |last=Star |first=John |url=http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2011_06_02_sfnmlb_slnmlb_1&mode=preview&vkey=preview_web_home&c_id=stl |title=Cardinals send Lynn to debut vs. Giants |website=MLB.com |date=June 1, 2011 |access-date=June 1, 2011 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304085257/http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2011_06_02_sfnmlb_slnmlb_1&mode=preview&vkey=preview_web_home&c_id=stl |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年他投了34.1局，送出40次三振。<ref name=scoutbio>{{cite web |url=http://stlcardinals.scout.com/a.z?s=321&p=8&c=1&nid=7431244 |title=Lance Lynn |publisher=[[Scout.com|Scout.com]] |access-date=June 21, 2014}}</ref>這年的國聯冠軍賽，林恩在第二場只投了一顆球就拿下勝投。<ref>{{cite news |last=Goold |first=Derrick |url=http://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/article_f29d3a5d-1228-52f8-a5d8-ecf2d5257129.html |title=Lynn proves his value to Cardinals as a reliever |newspaper=[[St._Louis_Post-Dispatch|St. Louis Post-Dispatch]] |date=October 11, 2011 |access-date=October 12, 2011 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111202449/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/article_f29d3a5d-1228-52f8-a5d8-ecf2d5257129.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>雖然他在世界大賽被[[艾德里安·貝爾垂|艾德里安·貝爾垂]]和[[尼爾森·克魯斯|尼爾森·克魯斯]]演出背靠背開轟給震撼教育，不過最終紅雀仍成功封王。

2012年，因為[[克里斯·卡本特|克里斯·卡本特]]進入傷兵名單，因此林恩遞補上先發輪值。而他在前六場先發也繳出1.40的防禦率，其中6月13日，他更是主投7.1局送出12次三振無失分奪勝。他也成為大聯盟第二位先達成10勝的投手。<ref>{{cite magazine |last=McNeal |first=Stan |url=http://aol.sportingnews.com/mlb/story/2012-06-13/lance-lynn-ra-dickey-10-wins-all-star-st-louis-cardinals-new-york-mets |title=Lance Lynn, unlikely Cardinals star, keeps pace with R.A. Dickey by registering 10th victory |magazine=[[Sporting_News|Sporting News]] |date=June 14, 2012 |access-date=June 14, 2012 |archive-date=2013-02-03 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130203060524/http://aol.sportingnews.com/mlb/story/2012-06-13/lance-lynn-ra-dickey-10-wins-all-star-st-louis-cardinals-new-york-mets |dead-url=no }}</ref>

林恩在上半年投出11勝7敗，防禦率3.41，他也因此成功入選明星賽。結果他在下半季表現判若兩人，他在下半季前8場先發防禦率高達5.23。8月防禦率更是高達6.66，他也因此被[[喬·凱利|喬·凱利]]取代先發位置。最終他拿下18勝7敗，防禦率3.78。<ref name=berra>{{cite web |last=Berra |first=Lindsay |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/lindsay-berra-st-louis-cardinals-pitcher-lance-lynn-gains-plenty-from-weight-loss?ymd=20131025&content_id=63333280 |title=Lighter on his feet, Lynn gains plenty from weight loss |website=MLB.com |date=October 25, 2013 |access-date=June 14, 2014 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714113334/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/lindsay-berra-st-louis-cardinals-pitcher-lance-lynn-gains-plenty-from-weight-loss?ymd=20131025&content_id=63333280 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[2012年國家聯盟冠軍賽|2012年國家聯盟冠軍賽]]，林恩在第五場擔任先發面對巨人，結果吞下敗投，最後紅雀在3勝1敗領先時遭到巨人逆轉淘汰。<ref name=berra/>

2013年，林恩開始減重。<ref name=berra/>他在這年拿下15勝10敗，防禦率3.97。<ref name=less>{{cite news |last=Goold |first=Derrick |url=http://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/less-is-more-for-lance-lynn/article_87874942-3de4-5763-a393-9ce51a420760.html |title=Less is more for Lance Lynn |newspaper=St. Louis Post-Dispatch |date=February 9, 2013 |access-date=June 14, 2014 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112064422/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/less-is-more-for-lance-lynn/article_87874942-3de4-5763-a393-9ce51a420760.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2014年–2017年====
2014年，林恩持續減重，而他在春訓比賽曾達成單場投出10次三振的紀錄，其中後面連續送出8次三振。<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Cocoran |first=Cliff |url=http://mlb.si.com/2014/03/14/lance-lynn-carlos-martinez-st-louis-cardinals-rotation-battle/ |title=Lance Lynn strikes out ten in four innings as Cardinals' rotation battle heats up |magazine=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]] |date=March 14, 2014 |access-date=April 13, 2014 |archive-date=2014-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140319082353/http://mlb.si.com/2014/03/14/lance-lynn-carlos-martinez-st-louis-cardinals-rotation-battle/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在4月14日面對釀酒人的比賽曾投出7局送出11次三振無失分的代表作。而他更是在4月19日敲出大聯盟首安。<ref>{{cite web |last=Langosch |first=Jenfier |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_04_19_slnmlb_wasmlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=stl |title=Lynn, Cruz battery powers Cards to victory |website=MLB.com |date=April 19, 2014 |access-date=April 19, 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233158/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_04_19_slnmlb_wasmlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=stl |dead-url=no }}</ref>

5月27日，他面對洋基隊投出生涯第一次完投勝。<ref>{{cite news |agency=Associated Press |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=340527124 |title=Cards blank Yanks as Lance Lynn tosses first career complete game |work=ESPN.com |date=May 27, 2014 |access-date=May 27, 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305131819/http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=340527124 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在6月23日達成生涯500次三振。<ref>{{cite news |agency=Associated Press |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2014/06/18/lynn-takes-heat-after-cardinals-lose-3-2-to-mets/10808205/ |title=Lynn takes heat after Cardinals lose 3–2 to Mets |newspaper=USA Today |date=June 18, 2014 |access-date=June 21, 2014 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111221408/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2014/06/18/lynn-takes-heat-after-cardinals-lose-3-2-to-mets/10808205/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>6月23日，他在有投手墳場之稱的庫爾斯球場先發面對洛磯隊，他主投8局無失分。<ref>{{cite web |last=Ulm |first=Cody |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_06_23_slnmlb_colmlb_1&mode=wrap#gid=2014_06_23_slnmlb_colmlb_1&mode=recap&c_id=stl |title=Adams homers twice behind Lynn's gem |website=MLB.com |date=June 23, 2014 |access-date=June 23, 2014 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714145508/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_06_23_slnmlb_colmlb_1&mode=wrap#gid=2014_06_23_slnmlb_colmlb_1&mode=recap&c_id=stl |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年紅雀隊再度闖進季後賽，林恩在國聯分區賽和國聯冠軍賽分別先發1場，防禦率為3.08。<ref>{{cite news |last=Gordon |first=Jeff |url=http://www.stltoday.com/gallery/sports/baseball/professional/cardinals-report-card/collection_3dcc54bf-d29e-5cde-b2c2-441460225311.html#15 |title=Cardinals 2014 report card: Lance Lynn A |newspaper=St. Louis Post-Dispatch |date=October 17, 2014 |access-date=October 18, 2014 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111163027/https://www.stltoday.com/gallery/sports/baseball/professional/cardinals-report-card/collection_3dcc54bf-d29e-5cde-b2c2-441460225311.html#15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年1月15日，林恩與紅雀簽下3年2200萬美元的延長合約。<ref>{{cite news |last=Goold |first=Derrick |url=http://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cards-lynn-agree-to--year-deal-for-million/article_8d31e606-49b3-5e85-b41d-edda7a7579e1.html |title=Cards, Lynn agree to 3-year deal for $22 million |newspaper=St. Louis Post-Dispatch |date=January 15, 2015 |access-date=August 14, 2015 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111192327/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cards-lynn-agree-to--year-deal-for-million/article_8d31e606-49b3-5e85-b41d-edda7a7579e1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=ESPN.com News Services |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/12172099/lance-lynn-st-louis-cardinals-agree-22-million-3-year-contract |title=Lance Lynn gets 3-year, $22M deal |work=ESPN.com |date=January 15, 2015 |access-date=August 14, 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306153302/http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/12172099/lance-lynn-st-louis-cardinals-agree-22-million-3-year-contract |dead-url=no }}</ref>4月15日，他拿下生涯50勝。<ref>{{cite web |last=Langosch |first=Jenifer |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/118614458/cardinals-lance-lynn-reaches-50-wins-in-99th-start |title=Lynn reaches 50 wins in 99th start |website=MLB.com |date=April 16, 2015 |access-date=July 18, 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081426/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/118614458/cardinals-lance-lynn-reaches-50-wins-in-99th-start |dead-url=no }}</ref>後來他在6月7日投球時右前臂感到緊繃，最後被放進傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web |last=Wilaj |first=Steve |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/132684366/lance-lynn-returns-from-injury-to-face-marlins |title=Lynn to return from DL for Miami series finale: Righty sidelined since June 8 with forearm strain |website=MLB.com |date=June 24, 2015 |access-date=June 24, 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304073518/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/132684366/lance-lynn-returns-from-injury-to-face-marlins |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在回歸大聯盟的首次先發便繳出主投6局無失分的成績。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Frisaro |first1=Joe |last2=Wilaj |first2=Steve |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/132890506/cardinals-back-lance-lynn-in-sweep-of-marlins?game_pk=414750 |title=Cardinals' bats back Lynn in sweep of Marlins |website=MLB.com |date=June 25, 2015 |access-date=June 25, 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060547/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/132890506/cardinals-back-lance-lynn-in-sweep-of-marlins?game_pk=414750 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月13日，林恩投出生涯最慘的一役。他僅投0.2局便狂丟7分。<ref>{{cite news |last=Nesbitt |first=Stephen |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/sports/pirates/2015/08/13/Pittsburgh-Pirates-score-early-late-to-beat-St-Louis-Cardinals-10-5-game-result-MLB-baseball/stories/201508130233 |title=Pirates score early, late to beat Cardinals, 10–5 |newspaper=[[Pittsburgh_Post-Gazette|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]] |date=August 13, 2015 |access-date=August 14, 2015 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112020902/https://www.post-gazette.com/sports/pirates/2015/08/13/Pittsburgh-Pirates-score-early-late-to-beat-St-Louis-Cardinals-10-5-game-result-MLB-baseball/stories/201508130233 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後他整年拿下12勝11敗，防禦率3.03。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=4&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=3,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2015 » Pitchers » Pitch Type Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-01-08 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109194030/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=4&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=3,d |dead-url=no }}</ref>隔年他更是動了湯米·約翰手術而整季報銷。<ref>{{cite web |last=Langosch |first=Jenifer |url=http://m.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article/156965640/lance-lynn-injured-has-tommy-john-surgery |title=Lynn has Tommy John surgery, will miss 2016 |website=MLB.com |date=November 10, 2015 |access-date=November 10, 2015 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107112257/http://m.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article/156965640/lance-lynn-injured-has-tommy-john-surgery/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年，林恩重返紅雀。該年他先發33場比賽，拿下11勝8敗，防禦率3.43。他的被打擊率2成44為全大聯盟最低，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=12,a |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2017 » Pitchers » Dashboard {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-01-08 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110003112/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=12,a |dead-url=no }}</ref>速球均速也領先大聯盟超過80%的投手。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=4&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=3,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2017 » Pitchers » Pitch Type Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-01-08 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110091542/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=4&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=3,d |dead-url=no }}</ref>球季結束後，林恩首次成為自由球員。
===明尼蘇達雙城===
2018年3月12日，林恩與雙城隊簽下1年1200萬美元的合約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/22716192/lance-lynn-minnesota-twins-reach-one-year-deal |title=Lance Lynn, Minnesota Twins reach one-year deal<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-01-08 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112115029/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/22716192/lance-lynn-minnesota-twins-reach-one-year-deal |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在雙城初登板第一局便狂丟五分，最後他在雙城留下7勝8敗，防禦率5.10的成績。

===紐約洋基===
2018年7月30日，雙城隊將林恩交易至洋基，換來[[泰勒·奧斯汀|泰勒·奧斯汀]]和Luis Rijo。<ref>{{cite web|title=Yankees trade for Lance Lynn from Twins for Tyler Austin and Luis Rijo|url=https://www.northjersey.com/story/sports/mlb/yankees/2018/07/30/new-york-yankees-trade-lance-lynn-twins-tyler-austin/868207002/|publisher=NorthJersey.com|access-date=July 30, 2018|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809004125/https://www.northjersey.com/story/sports/mlb/yankees/2018/07/30/new-york-yankees-trade-lance-lynn-twins-tyler-austin/868207002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>洋基原本打算將林恩放在牛棚擔任長中繼，<ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/nationals/yanks-deal-adam-warren-tyler-austin-and-acquire-lance-lynn/2018/07/30/a00009aa-945f-11e8-818b-e9b7348cd87d_story.html</ref>不過在[[桑尼·葛雷|桑尼·葛雷]]陷入低潮期間，林恩擔任了洋基先發投手。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bronxpinstripes.com/news-rumors/sonny-gray-bumped-from-yankees-rotation-lance-lynn-to-take-his-place/ |title=Sonny Gray bumped from Yankees' rotation, Lance Lynn to take his place<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-01-08 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109194040/http://bronxpinstripes.com/news-rumors/sonny-gray-bumped-from-yankees-rotation-lance-lynn-to-take-his-place/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===德州遊騎兵===
2018年12月18日，林恩與遊騎兵隊簽下3年3千萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/rangers-sign-pitcher-lance-lynn/c-301973844|title=Rangers sign right-hander Lynn to 3-year deal|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|date=December 18, 2018|access-date=December 18, 2018|archive-date=2018-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181219005422/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/rangers-sign-pitcher-lance-lynn/c-301973844|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，他投出16勝11敗，防禦率3.67。但他也投出大聯盟最多的18次暴投，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/MLB/2019-pitching-leaders.shtml |title=2019 Major League Baseball Pitching Leaders |website=Baseball-Reference.com |access-date=2019-10-09 |archive-date=2019-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009080225/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/MLB/2019-pitching-leaders.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>而他在美聯賽揚獎票選拿下第五名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bbwaa.com/19-al-cy/|title=Justin Verlander edges Astros teammate to win 2nd Cy Young Award|website=[[Baseball_Writers'_Association_of_America|Baseball Writers' Association of America]]|date=November 13, 2019|access-date=November 13, 2019|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205010918/https://bbwaa.com/19-al-cy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年8月9日，林恩投出生涯100勝。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/lance-lynn-rangers-earn-sweep-of-angels | title=Lynn earns 100th win, Rangers sweep Halos | work=MLB.com | author=T.R. Sullivan | date=August 9, 2020 | access-date=August 11, 2020 | archive-date=2021-01-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109233759/https://www.mlb.com/rangers/news/lance-lynn-rangers-earn-sweep-of-angels | dead-url=no }}</ref>
===芝加哥白襪===
2020年12月7日，白襪隊用新秀[[丹恩·唐寧|丹恩·唐寧]]和Avery Weems向遊騎兵交易林恩。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/lance-lynn-white-sox-trade|title=White Sox acquire Lance Lynn|date=December 7, 2020|access-date=December 8, 2020|archive-date=2021-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331170501/https://www.mlb.com/news/lance-lynn-white-sox-trade|dead-url=no}}</ref>

