而他從小是一名洋基球迷。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newsday.com/sports/baseball/yankees/lance-lynn-making-his-dad-and-yankees-happy-he-s-here-1.20424556 |title=Lance Lynn making his dad and Yankees happy he's here |newspaper=Newsday |date=2018-08-11 |access-date=2019-10-09 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110130219/https://www.newsday.com/sports/baseball/yankees/lance-lynn-making-his-dad-and-yankees-happy-he-s-here-1.20424556 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
